=== Transportation ===
* From {{ill|lt=Iwaki Station|Q5353428|WD=Q5353428|1=Iwaki Station (Fukushima)}} on the {{ill|lt=Jōban Line|Q1369263|WD=Q1369263|1=Jōban Line}}, take {{ill|lt=Shin Jōban Kōtsū|Q11502130|WD=Q11502130|1=Shin Joban Kotsu}} bus bound for Nishihara via Natsui, get off at "Ōkunitama Shrine" bus stop
* 1 minute by car from the grade-separated junction of {{ill|lt=National Route 6|Q1038714|WD=Q1038714|1=Japan National Route 6}} {{ill|lt=Jōban Bypass|Q11481556|WD=Q11481556|1=Tokiwa bypass}} and {{ill|lt=Fukushima Prefectural Route 229 Kabutozuka Kofun Line|Q11593467|WD=Q11593467|1=Fukushima Prefectural Road Route 229}}

